model

Interface IContextPanelNode

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IProductContainer
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ProductContainer, ProductGroup, StorageUnit, StorageUnits

    public interface IContextPanelNode
    This interface allows the data structures to communicate with the gui. some of the methods are pointless for certain instances. For example getThreeMonthSupply will always return null for StorageUnit but it is included to help ease interaction with the gui.
    Author:
    Kevin
